This the installion guide for Industrial chatbot running in local system.
==================================================

Required tool and libraries:
1. Anaconda3(64-bit) with jupyter installed in it
2. nltk and tkinter libraries should be pre installed.
    Instructions to install libraries before the run if above libraries are not installed:
        ! pip install --upgrade category_encoders
        !python -m nltk.downloader stopwords
        !python -m nltk.downloader punkt


===================================================
1. Open 'Chatbot gui.ipynb' in jupyter notebook or 'Chatbot gui.py' in spyder.
2. Run all the cells and a chatbot window will popup.
3. Valid input should be given in the format as given in the dataset. Any invalid input with throw callback error.